Title: Computations Around Bayesian Predictive Power
Version: 1.0.6
Date: 2025-02-21
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Kaspar", family = "Rufibach", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "kaspar.rufibach@gmail.com"),
